data.title: Information about a software update of Acuson Antares and Sonoline Antares ultrasound devices of Siemens
data.meta_description: Siemens has issued an information about a software update of Acuson Antares and Sonoline Antares ultrasound devices due to the potential risk of right-left reversed subsidiary lines.
